    "year": 2026,
    "status": "Completed",
    "service": "Multi Townhouse Development",
    "area": "559.50 sqm",
    "summary": "Running alongside one of Melbourne's active rail corridors, this townhouse development takes its energy directly from its setting rather than shielding itself from it. Where a quieter suburban site might call for a more introspective architecture, here the constant presence of movement, trains, pedestrians, the shifting rhythm of daily commuting, becomes a legitimate design driver in its own right. 2Form Consulting's design approach establishes a strong visual and spatial connection between the public streetscape and the private life of the dwelling. The architecture celebrates movement as a defining design driver, translating into composition that animates the building and contributes to the evolving urban landscape.",
